    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Primula \u00d7 brueggeri are fever and rheumatism, which are alleviated through the plant's anti-inflammatory properties. Primula \u00d7 brueggeri has been used to treat digestive issues such as diarrhea and constipation by regulating bowel movements and reducing inflammation in the intestines. This plant has also been employed to address respiratory problems like bronchitis, which is characterized by its ability to thin mucus and ease congestion. In addition, Primula \u00d7 brueggeri has been used to treat wounds and skin conditions by promoting tissue repair and reducing pain. Furthermore, its antiseptic properties have made it a useful remedy for infections such as septicemia.",
