    "properties_description": "The main therapeutic properties of Primula \u00d7 brueggeri are its anti-inflammatory activity, which makes it useful in the treatment of various inflammatory conditions, such as arthritis and gout. Antimicrobial properties of this plant enable it to inhibit the growth of microorganisms, including bacteria and fungi, thereby preventing infections. Its antioxidant capacity helps to protect cells from oxidative damage, which can contribute to the development of various diseases. The plant's antiviral properties have been shown to inhibit the replication of certain viruses, including herpes simplex virus and influenza virus. Additionally, Primula \u00d7 brueggeri has been found to possess hepatoprotective properties, which can help to prevent liver damage and promote liver health.",
